screen_desc: The screenshot displays the menu interface for "Bradman Pizza House," featuring a rating of 4.7 from over 200 ratings. Featured items include "Chicken Parmigiana" priced at A$27.90, marked as the most liked item with a 93% approval rating from 43 reviews, and "Garlic Bread" priced at A$5.20, the second most liked item with an 88% approval rating from 35 reviews. The interface also shows a section for reviews, indicating 44 public reviews.
